===Adverb===
{{en-adv|-}}

# {{context|conjunctive}} [[despite|Despite]] that; [[however]].
#: ''I will do it, '''though'''.''
# {{context|degree}} Used to intensify statements or questions; [[indeed]].
#: ''"Man, it's hot in here." — "Isn't it, '''though'''?"''

